  <brief_title>Clinical Study Examining the Safety and Efficacy of Doxorubicin Drug Eluting Microspheres Transarterial Embolization in the Setting of Hepatocellular Carcinoma (HCC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I/II Study Examining Pharmacokinetics, Adverse Events, and Surgically Resected Histopathological Response Utilizing a Dose Escalation Model of Doxorubicin Loaded Drug Eluting Superabsorbent Polymer Microspheres in Surgically Resectable Hepatocellular Carcinoma in Humans</official_title>
